    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. Transcript API Request\n- Calls **youtube-transcript.io**\n- Does not require YouTube OAuth\n- Returns the response (Full Response + text)\n- The next node performs robust parsing",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 280,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "c4fd578a-b9af-4aab-bc36-1f2781804826",
      "name": "Sticky Note - API",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1680,
        688
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3. Parsing & Cleaning\n- Parses JSON even when the response arrives as a string (using safe parsing / try-catch) \n- Supports multiple response shapes (`text` / `transcript` / `tracks`)\n- Basic cleaning:\n  - `\\n` → space\n  - Collapses repeated whitespace\n  - Removes `[Music]` / `[Música]`\n\nOutput: text ready for AI processing\n",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 640,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "8700f14e-75cc-4382-b9e4-f4a23587f597",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Processing",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        2368,
